### Get all applications
GET http://localhost:5000/applications

### Create application
POST http://localhost:5000/applications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "company": "Epic Systems",
  "position": "Software Developer",
  "location": "Madison, WI",
  "salary": 85000,
  "status": "Applied",
  "dateApplied": "2026-03-07",
  "notes": "Applied through careers page",
  "userId": 1
}

### Update application
PUT http://localhost:5000/applications/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "company": "Epic Systems",
  "position": "Software Developer",
  "location": "Madison, WI",
  "salary": 90000,
  "status": "Interview",
  "dateApplied": "2026-03-07",
  "notes": "Moved to interview stage"
}

### Delete application
DELETE http://localhost:5000/applications/3